00:36:50,789 --> 00:36:52,552
Are you listening?

372
00:37:03,435 --> 00:37:04,993
My name is Lily.

373
00:37:06,271 --> 00:37:08,136
I have a daughter.

374
00:37:10,442 --> 00:37:12,774
I'm recently divorced.

375
00:37:13,611 --> 00:37:15,476
Have you been married?

376
00:37:17,081 --> 00:37:18,878
Do you have family?

377
00:37:19,451 --> 00:37:21,544
Do they come to visit you?

378
00:37:25,256 --> 00:37:26,985
Can you hear me?

379
00:37:59,390 --> 00:38:03,190
What? Just a second.

380
00:38:05,763 --> 00:38:09,358
Jack? What did you say?

381
00:38:12,370 --> 00:38:14,804
Married? But you told me....

382
00:38:17,575 --> 00:38:20,043
We agreed
we'd never marry anyone.

383
00:38:23,681 --> 00:38:26,172
Do you realize what you've done?

384
00:38:26,651 --> 00:38:30,883
It's pouring, and I can't find a cab.
I can't get home.

385
00:38:31,155 --> 00:38:32,747
