when I need someone?

388
00:38:44,903 --> 00:38:47,167
I knew this would happen.

389
00:38:51,643 --> 00:38:54,009
<i>Hello? Xiang?</i>

390
00:38:54,812 --> 00:38:56,336
<i>Are you there?</i>

391
00:38:57,749 --> 00:38:59,478
<i>Hello?</i>

392
00:39:05,023 --> 00:39:06,718
<i>Xiang.</i>

393
00:39:53,504 --> 00:39:56,598
Mom, why do I have to
study piano?

394
00:39:56,774 --> 00:40:00,608
A girl needs a backup.

395
00:40:00,812 --> 00:40:02,643
If your husband
ever leaves you...

396
00:40:03,214 --> 00:40:05,774
...you can teach piano
to support yourself.

397
00:40:05,950 --> 00:40:10,580
-But why would he leave me?
-Who knows?

398
00:40:11,089 --> 00:40:14,058
At least you'll be prepared.

399
00:40:16,928 --> 00:40:18,452
Carry on!

400
